description: Special edition of "Kentucky Nightmare"--with commentary provided by the show producers' mothers.
title: Momentary
tags: space ghost c2c episode 82 mommentary part 1

description: The creators of Space Ghost Coast to Coast did not have enough time to finish the show.  So, here, watch this rough cut.
title: Live at the Filmore
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 89 live at the filmore

description: Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin! Evil Twin!
title: Switcheroo
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 26 switcheroo evil twin susan olsen elvira

description: Space Ghost's obsession with hair care products finally gets him into trouble when he lathers up with Chambraigne, the shampoo for your brain. Despite limb loss, Space Ghost tries to convince Bob Costas and the world that Chambraigne truly is an intelli-hancer. Then Carl explodes.
title: Chambraigne
tags: Space Ghost episode 69 Chambraigne

description: Performance artist Laurie Anderson riles Space Ghost by revealing that she never watches television, then waxes conspiratorial about cyberspace. A disengaged Space Ghost invisos out, missing much of their remaining conversation. Next, Space Ghost endeavors to understand members of the performance troupe Stomp.
title: Art Show
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 32 art show laurie anderson stomp

description: Moltar gets his chance to host the show while Space Ghost illegally copies the new Radiohead album.  Later, it is revealed that Space Ghost is married to Bjork.  Space Ghost ends the episode by knocking her off of a cliff.
title: Knifin' Around
tags: space ghost c2c episode 79 knifin' around

description: Desperate for a new gig, Space Ghost kisses up to "Talk Soup" host John Henson and "Entertainment Tonight" host Bob Goen by telling each that they are "pretty men." Space Ghost even offers to set Henson up with his "sister" Judy. Brak spoils the affair by spilling gravy all over the set.
title: Suckup
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 52 suckup talk soup john henson bob goen

description: After revealing that contractual squabbles before the premiere of "Space Ghost Coast to Coast" resulted in an aborted test shoot starring rival superhero Birdman, host Lokar presents exclusive glimpses of this "lost" pilot.
title: Pilot
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 39 pilot lokar birdman american gladiators

description: Sonic Youth's Thurston Moore stars as Fred Cracklin in a 15-minute showcase for late musician Sonny Sharrock. Sharrock was the man behind the "Space Ghost Coast to Coast" theme music.
title: Sharrock

description: Zorak is zapped until he can apparently no longer regenerate, leaving Space Ghost without a bandleader. Moltar is instructed to fill in for his dearly departed friend by singing renditions of German folk songs, which puts Beck, the show's lone guest, to sleep.
title: Edelweiss
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 36 edelweiss zorak bandleader beck

description: Grandpa Space Ghost, whose physique is identical to his grandson's and whose voice is identical to WCW wrestler "Macho Man" Randy Savage, gives an "OOOO-YEEAAAHHH!" performance despite being clubbed with a chair by Zorak. Grandpa Ghostal interviews kid actress Raven Symone.
title: Piledriver
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 51 piledriver macho man randy savage grandpa leonard ghostal raven symone

description: No one sings the blues like Zorak. From the 1997 album Space Ghost's Musical Bar-B-Que.
title: Zorak: Zingor

description: After model Cyndi Guyer, the female Fabio, explains what she looks for in a man, the Jerky Boys arrive and promptly threaten to punch Space Ghost in the mouth. The undertow of violence subsides with the appearance of model Dian Parkinson.
title: Punch
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c punch episode 7

description: Space Ghost adds a few new twists: a live studio audience, a remarkably versatile applause sign and viewer call-in. The results fall flat and Space Ghost isn't happy. Palmer Mills and Sandra Bernhard come to agree Space Ghost is a jerk.
title: Jerk

description: Space Ghost pays tribute to Women in the Entertainment Industry. Fran Drescher paralyzes Space Ghost with desire. Carol Channing dispenses advice to soothe his heart but this comfort is ruined by the appearance of rocker Alice Cooper.
title: Girlie Show
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c girlie show episode 13

description: It's mating season on Zorak's home planet. Despite the role the male plays in the love ritual, Zorak gives in to the common of insect impulses and returns home. Space Ghost welcomes Catherine Bach and plays the blues with Matthew Sweet.
title: Urges

description: Space Ghost turns to experts for advice on supernatural phenomena such as the disappearance of his phantom cruiser keys. Michael Norman, ghost expert and author of Historic Haunted America, and Bill Nye are all too happy to help him out.
title: Boo!

description: Space Ghost's sidekicks have hosted a convention behind his back. Moltar and Zorak bring out their own guests Bill Mumy and Mark Hamill. In a jealous rage, Space Ghost announces plans for Space Ghost Con '97, vowing to exclude his co-stars.
title: Switcheroo '97
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 42 switcheroo ii sidekicks bill mumy will robinson lost in space mark hamill con

description: With Moltar on the run, Space Ghost is forced to recruit Tansut as his fill-in director, who causes problems before bringing out guests Kirk Hammett and James Hetfield of Metallica.
title: Jacksonville
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 29 jacksonville james hetfield metallica kirk hammett

description: Reggae star Jimmy Cliff chats with Space Ghost about his new album and touring in South America. Moltar and mechanic-turned-musician Jack Logan share a creepy conversation about items underneath their beds.
title: Speck
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 40 speck reggae jimmy cliff jack logan eye

description: Space Ghost Coast to Coast welcomes its first-ever Academy Award winner, Charlton Heston, who, after much prodding, offers his trophy to Space Ghost.
title: Dam
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 53 dam charlton heston

description: Even though two prominent rappers, Ice-T and Ernie-C, make their 'Space Ghost Coast to Coast' debut, Space Ghost decides to do the 'hip shake' throughout the show. Zorak attempts to hypnotize all the guests, including actor Fred Willard.
title: Needledrop
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode needledrop 46 ice-t ernie c rappers fred willard

description: Indie rock group Pavement, sitting in for an incarcerated Zorak and The Original Way-Outs, makes history as the first band ever to perform on Space Ghost Coast to Coast.
title: Pavement
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 48 pavement goldie hawn tommy davidson red green colin quinn

description: Space Ghost, an unofficial member of the P-Funk Mob, sets the groove in motion with George Clinton, but Moltar attempts to wrest the show from Space Ghost's control so he can interview his hero and the star of TV's 'CHiPs,' Erik Estrada.
title: Untitled
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 49 untitled parliament funkadelic george clinton erik estrada chips

description: The deep space set comes alive like never before with 11 glorious musical numbers. Space Ghost, Zorak and Moltar are joined by Brak, who performs a melodic Man on the Street duet with the originator of the popular skit, Steve Allen.
title: Boat Show
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 54 boatshow steve allen musical andy dick

description: When the Council of Doom takes your phone calls and the only caller is Brak posing as Seymour Hiney, you know your telethon is in trouble. It takes Space Ghost until the telethon's ending to realize his show is completely bankrupt for good!
title: Telethon
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 55 telethon seymour hiney brak birdman

description: Space Ghost and Zorak try to endorse ointment and potted meat to the home viewing audience. Pat Boone sings Space Ghost's praises, while rapper Chuck D is not impressed with the public-service rap performance by the Rappin' Space Goblin.
title: Dimethyl Pyrimidinol Bisulfite
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 56 Dimethylpyrimidinol Bisulfite ointment pat boone chuck d

description: A marketing infomercial about taking advantage of Space Ghost's power, followed by interviews with the winners of the "Haiku'n for Space Ghost" contest.
title: Joshua
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 57 joshua haiku tony bennett tom arnold

description: Space Ghost grows angry upon learning that he has been 'imposternated' on a bizarre, intergalactic television program called 'The Warren Show.' In response, he takes Moltar and Zorak on a mission to find the host, who is actually a bush.
title: Warren
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 62 warren bush

description: Space Ghost announces he is dying and begins to look for someone to replace him. To confirm the grim prognosis, Dr. Drew Pinsky appears on the show. Zorak becomes excited and begins playing New Orleans jazz, which gets him zapped.
title: Terminal
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 58 terminal dying dr drew pinsky

description: Space Ghost is the target of a lawsuit filed against him by former co-stars Jan and Jace. The twins employ the services of the infamous Dr. Nightmare to represent their case. Space Ghost acquires attorney Greta Van Susteren.
title: Lawsuit
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 60 lawsuit jan jace lawyer dr nightmare great van susteren

description: Space Ghost attempts to take Ghost Planet to the United States, and consequently focuses the show on various aspects of America. Zorak fools Space Ghost into thinking that his mantis droppings are his children.
title: Intense Patriotism

description: Supermodel Tyra Banks guests on an episode that features Space Ghost trading Moltar to a Japanese baseball team. Moltar is replaced in the control room by a dog and has a song dedicated to him by Zorak.
title: Chinatown
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 63 chinatown japan baseball tyra banks

description: Pursuing a movie career, Space Ghost seeks advice from the director of 'Mall Rats,' Kevin Smith, and actor Ben Stiller. Hollywood director Jim Jarmusch also makes an appearance.
title: Rio Ghosto
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 64 rio ghosto mallrats kevin smith ben stiller jim jarmusch

description: Joey, an overzealous ex-intern, annoys Space Ghost with his antics. In retribution, Space Ghost destroys the pest and shuttles his corpse into outer space for disposal.
title: Pal Joey
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 65 pal joey intern fired michael moore

description: Space Ghost has a temper tantrum and he leaves the show.  While he's gone, Zorak, Moltar and Dave Thomas have a great time.  Meanwhile, Space Ghost tries to make friends with the superheroes at the Hole of Justice, but they beat him up.
title: The Justice Hole
tags: space ghost c2c episode 78 justice hole

description: Space Ghost is angry about a variety of topics, and rants mightily to his guest, comedian Dennis Miller.
title: Whipping Post
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 84 whipping post dennis miller

description: Lokar hosts a clip show while Space Ghost visits his mother in Florida.
title: Le Livre D' Histoire

title: Zorak & Diamond Dallas Page: Evil is Only Skin Deep

description: Musician Jonathan Richman, who first climbed to fame fronting The Modern Lovers, favors Space Ghost with a couple of charming songs during a meandering conversation.
title: Transcript

description: Moltar and Zorak compete for Space Ghost's attention, while Space Ghost is more concerned with the safety of comedian Todd Barry's automobile.
title: Eat a Peach
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 85 eat a peach todd barry

description: Marshall "Duh" Staxx of the musical group Green Jelly and yodeller Wylie Gustafson are the freaks du jour in this aptly named episode. The show also features a video pirate who identifies himself only as "Commander Andy of the Cosmos."
title: Freak Show

description: Space Ghost is afflicted by the Curse of Kintave and is driven to eat all of his guests. In the end, even Zorak and Moltar cannot escape his ravenous appetite. The svelte Shirley Manson is spared, since she's not much of a meal.
title: Curses

description: Girl hair. Hanson has it and Space Ghost is obsessed with combing it. This episode reveals Space Ghost's dark side as well as Zorak's desire to procure teeth so that he can get into clubs. Appearances by the Tooth Fairy and Santa bring about one of the weirdest scenes yet staged on the show.
title: Girl Hair
tags: Space Ghost Episode 71 Girl Hair

description: Self-heralded "comedy ghetto" resident Michael McKean barely gets a word in with Space Ghost, and David Lander suffers a similar fate. The reason? Zorak and Space Ghost's roommate tiff spilling over into the show. In addition, a menacing "kitty" blimp hovers around Ghost Planet.
title: Boo Boo Kitty
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 45 boo boo kitty michael mckean david lander blimp

description: Space Ghost welcomes shiny happy Michael Stipe from R.E.M. (Space Ghost: "Is that you in the corner?"Stipe: "Yes, it is.") Later, he shares time-honored difficult-places-to-reach-while-scratching-stories with Lassie. Mujibur and Sirajul, frequent guest stars on "The Late Show with David Letterman,"mysteriously appear with Space Ghost's pizza.
title: Hungry
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c hungry episode 14

description: Space Ghost introduces "Space Time Quiz Fun 9000" and his "contestants," comedians David Cross and Bob Odenkirk of HBO's "Mr. Show." What follows is a rapid-fire conversation in more ways than one, as Odenkirk's growing addiction to power-band blasts results in a steady volley from Space Ghost.
title: Gallagher
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 35 gallagher bob odenkirk david cross mr show

description: Hoping to rehabilitate Zorak, Space Ghost welcomes psychiatrist Dr. Joyce Brothers, who ends up being more concerned about him. Later, comic Rich Hall give Space Ghost pointers on how to pick up women that are immediately used by Zorak and Moltar to impress author Anka Radakovich.
title: Self Help
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c self help episode 9

description: The comedy stakes are high when Space Ghost, Moltar, Zorak and guest Steven Wright are stalked by body-snatching pods. Show producers auctioned off the ending of this episode on eBay.
title: Snatch
tags: Space Ghost Episode 70 Snatch

description: After declaring his fondness for Mexican food, Space Ghost asks diet guru Susan Powter what super powers help "stop the insanity."  Comedian Kevin Meaney discusses the virtues of wearing tight pants and the Bee Gees stop by for a short, bizarre visit.
title: Spanish Translation
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 1 spanish translation susan powter

description: Space Ghost is hosting a "mystery dinner theater" and the guest star is Busta Rhymes.  After causing a massive gas leak, Space Ghost beats Zorak senseless a number of times.  Later, they end up at a grocery store, confusing it for a hospital.
title: Flipmode
tags: space ghost c2c episode 80 flipmode

description: Space Ghost chats with Robin Leach until his guest reveals that he is, in fact, an evil villain named Zoltran. Leach, as Zoltran, blasts Space Ghost by shooting lasers out of his eyes. Unfortunately for Space Ghost, the show doesn't get any easier as Merrill Markoe needles him about his age and his intergalactic location.
title: Zoltran
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 38 zoltran robin leach merrill markoe

description: Space Ghost shows off his versatility by emceeing Cartoon Network's "World Premiere Toon In".  Members of the Council of Doom appear as judges in a beauty pageant-style competition between five cartoon directors. Blip also makes an appearance, prompting Space Ghost to croon, "Oh, what a monkey he is!"
title: President's Day Nightmare
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c president's day nightmare

description: After Moltar sends Space Ghost away to "pick up an important package in the mailroom," Zorak takes a seat behind the desk. What happens next is television history as Zorak cackles through a rapid-fire series of "interviews" with everyone from actress Cameron Diaz to TV's Jimmie "Good Times" Walker.
title: Surprise

description: The rapport between Branford Marsalis and Space Ghost makes it look as though the then-band leader of "The Tonight Show"might be switching talk shows. Next, a child star from the same television era as Space Ghost, Danny Bonaduce, talks about his days with the Partridge family and his deep-seated hatred for Osmonds.
title: Gum, Disease
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c gum disease episode 10

description: This loose parody of Stanley Kubrick's "2001: A Space Odyssey" features Joel Hodgson, creator of "Mystery Science Theater 3000," and comedic magicians Penn and Teller. Moltar and Zorak are fired when Space Ghost replaces them with MOE 2000, an unfeeling computer director.

This flashback episode transports viewers to a dress rehearsal two days before the premiere of "Space Ghost Coast to Coast" in April 1994. Offering a rare glimpse behind the scenes, "Rehearsal" features Space Ghost, Moltar and Zorak flubbing familiar gags, missing cues and mistiming special effects.
title: Rehearsal
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 34 rehearsal flashback fred schneider moltar zorak

description: Space Ghost gets hammered during his interview with Jeff Probst, the host of TV's "Survivor".
title: Idlewild South
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 87 idlewild south jeff probst survivor

description: Space Ghost welcomes fellow intergalactic entertainer William Shatner, but their interview is cut short when Space Ghost is called into action to take part in an epic space battle.
title: In Memory of Elizabeth Reed
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 86 in memory of elizabeth reed william shatner

description: Lokar, a villain from Space Ghost's original series, attempts to woo Moltar away from his helm as director. Oblivious, Space Ghost proceeds with his celebrity guests--Terry Jones and Glen Phillips--one of whom reveals his secret identity as Tongue Man.
title: Explode

description: Feeling a little wired, Space Ghost asks professional wrestler Hulk Hogan to put him in a sleeper hold so that he can get some rest. Instead, Hogan recites an original haiku about Zorak. Slash from Guns 'N' Roses winds up the show with his usual gift for gab.
title: Sleeper

description: After Space Ghost declares his love for Merill Markoe, he receives advice from Adam Corolla, host of MTV's "Loveline." Knowing that Space Ghost is smitten, Zorak begins to do everything in his power to win Merrill Markoe as his own, leading to a battle between the two.
title: Toast
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 59 toast merill markoe adam corolla

description: Jon Benjamin, voice of Ben Katz on Comedy Central's "Dr. Katz,"guests on a show that features rare appearances by Brak and Tansut.
title: King Dead
tags: space ghost c2c episode 76 king dead jon benjamin dr katz

description: Space Ghost marks a "special notch in the belt that is the Space Ghost saga" with returning guests Bobcat Goldthwait and Judy Tenuda. The show also includes special appearances by villian-turned-announcer Tansut and the evil Chad Ghostal, as well as a spectacular career retrospective montage compiled by Moltar.
title: Anniversary
tags: sgc2c space ghost coast to coast episode 37 anniversary bobcat goldthwait just tenuda tansut chad ghostal

description: Space Ghost interviews Denis Leary with questions like, "Are you a leprechaun?" Moltar destroys Ghost Planet and Space Ghost subsequently appears at a day camp, explaining how he saved Christmas.
title: Waiting for Edward

description: After a show open that features Moltar and Zorak arguing the respective merits of Beefaroni and Beefaghetti, Space Ghost enlists the Council of Doom to judge an old-fashioned cooking competition between three nationally-acclaimed culinary experts: Emeril Lagasse, Nathalie Dupree and Martin Yan.
title: Cookout
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 31 cookout beefaroni beefaghetti emeril lagasse martin yen nathalie dupree council of doom

description: "Beavis and Butthead" and "King of the Hill" creator Mike Judge kindly asks Space Ghost to "whack the Rugrats." Space Ghost agrees to the job, as long as he can get onto one of Judge's shows. Harland Williams doesn't last long after calling Space Ghost "Billy" and "Naughty Space Ghost."
title: Sphinx
tags: space ghost coast to coast sgc2c episode 47 sphinx beavis butthead mike judge harland williams

description: Former "Late Show With David Letterman" writers scripted this unabashed spoof of late-night talk show convention. Janeane Garofalo reveals her secret power, then hypnotist Flip Orley joins Space Ghost until Zorak, using an incantation, turns him into David Grohl of the Foo Fighters. Sitting in with the band is John Popper of Blues Traveler.
title: Late Show
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 30 late show david letterman janeane garofalo flip orley dave grohl john popper foo fighters blues traveler

description: A mysterious villain kidnaps Moltar and Space Ghost must solicit the help of Adam West, Lee Meriweather and Eartha Kitt, all from the "Batman"television series, in an effort to save him. And...holy exoskeleton, Space Ghost, it's Zorak as Batmantis!
title: Batmantis
tags: space ghost coast to coast c2c batmantis episode 8

description: Learn how to win any argument.
title: Shut Up

description: Debuting on Valentine's Day, this episode finds Space Ghost heartbroken over a failed relationship. The despondent Ghost finds that not even the antics of comedian Carrot Top can lure him from his lovesick stupor.
title: Lovesick

description: Space Ghost loses the show to the owner of a liquor store, and he is forced to use a shark as the show's new mascot.  A bear wanders onto the set, upsetting the normal routine by repeatedly attacking Space Ghost.  Later, the shark explodes, attracting giant Space Bees.
title: Kentucky Nightmare
tags: space ghost c2c episode 77 kentucky nightmare

description: In an apparent tribute to E! Entertainment's well-publicized re-enactments of the O.J. Simpson hearings, viewers are treated to performances of selected "Space Ghost Coast to Coast" moments by the Ghost Planet Dinner Theater Ensemble of Doraville, GA.
title: Woody Allen's Fall Project
tags: space ghost coast to coast episode 33 woody allen's fall project simpson oj james kirkconnell

description: Space Ghost gets down and dirty with Triumph, the dog who loves to piss everyone off.
title: Dreams
tags: space ghost c2c sg episode 88 dreams triumph the insult comic dog

description: Space Ghost and talk show host Conan O'Brien are engaged in riveting and witty repartee when a fire ant bites Space Ghost and everything goes Dada.
title: Fire Ant- Short Version

description: The writing and production staff of "Space Ghost Coast to Coast" join voice talents C. Martin Croker (Zorak and Moltar) and George Lowe (Space Ghost) to read through a script of an episode entitled "Fire Ant."
title: Table Read
tags: Space Ghost Episode 74 Table Read
